2
00:00:04,300 --> 00:00:06,410
In the first part of this course,

3
00:00:06,410 --> 00:00:11,980
you'll learn how to integrate the Apache PDFBox API to your Java application.

4
00:00:11,980 --> 00:00:17,790
As the first step, you'll configure the API in a Java project.

5
00:00:17,790 --> 00:00:23,240
Then go ahead and create your very first PDF document.

6
00:00:23,240 --> 00:00:29,040
Go a few more steps ahead and modify the PDF document that you created.

7
00:00:29,040 --> 00:00:36,340
And finally, you'll spend some time looking at some advanced features of the API.

8
00:00:36,340 --> 00:00:39,370
Hope the journey's quite interesting so far.

9
