10
00:00:45,740 --> 00:00:48,700
Your starting point will be to configure the API,

11
00:00:48,700 --> 00:00:53,130
and thereafter you'll go straight ahead to work with Microsoft

12
00:00:53,130 --> 00:00:57,970
Office documents by creating and modifying Excel,

13
00:00:57,970 --> 00:01:01,240
Word, and PowerPoint documents.

14
00:01:01,240 --> 00:01:03,220
By the end of this course,

15
00:01:03,220 --> 00:01:10,640
you'll have mastered Apache PDFBox and POI API integrations in Java.

16
00:01:10,640 --> 00:01:15,540
Now, let's take a look at the agenda of the first part of the course.

17
