You will outline the essentials of the Apache PDFBox library in

19
00:01:23,700 --> 00:01:28,440
terms of what it offers you, its components, and common

20
00:01:28,440 --> 00:01:33,750
applications. Configure the development environment to be able

21
00:01:33,750 --> 00:01:37,240
to use it in a Java application.

22
00:01:37,240 --> 00:01:38,390
Thereafter,

23
00:01:38,390 --> 00:01:45,140
you will create your very first PDF document and start adding content to it.

24
00:01:45,140 --> 00:01:51,360
Then you'll see how to modify and already create a PDF by loading,

25
00:01:51,360 --> 00:01:57,340
